OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWelsh councils could face  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbankruptcy, leaders warn   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It's only a matter of time before a    
OL,6, Welsh council goes bankrupt unless cash
OL,7, pressures ease, bosses have said.      
OL,9,FAnthony Hunt, Labour leader of Torfaen 
OL,10,Fcouncil, said "the very fabric of our  
OL,11,Flocal public services is under threat".
OL,13,FAnd Mark Pritchard, independent leader 
OL,14,Fof Wrexham council, said it faced      
OL,15,Fcutting community care help that would 
OL,16,Fhave a negative impact on NHS services.
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said it would     
OL,19,Fcontinue to work closely with councils 
OL,20,Fto "meet the shared challenges".       
